snippet.title: AVIAN - Release Teaser
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD GAME : https://royale-monkey.itch.io/avian

Here is the trailer of our game AVIAN, a music-based exploration game in which you can play the flute. This game is a student project made in 6 months and it represents only a vertical slice of our final product. Please, feel free to give us your feedback in the comments

Twitter : https://twitter.com/royale_monkey
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/studioroyalemonkey/
Reddit : https://www.reddit.com/user/Royale-Monkey
